Haru no Yume means 'dream of spring.'

Our dream is that you will fall in love with our food.

Haru no Yume creates authentic Japanese cuisine that is  beautifully presented to offer pleasure for all your senses.

Our Chefs use traditional Japanese cooking methods with a modern twist. 

In 2009, we opened our first restaurant in Mt. Eden and now have another restaurant near Victoria Park in Central Auckland. 
We invite you to enjoy the finest Japanese dining experience in Auckland. Come on in and have a great time. 




